  <name>WorkraveQt</name>
  <summary>RSI prevention tool - take regular breaks</summary>
  
  <description>
    <p>
      WorkraveQt is a modern reimplementation of Workrave in Qt. It is designed 
      to help prevent Repetitive Strain Injury (RSI) by reminding you to take 
      regular breaks from your computer.
    </p>
    <p>
      Unlike the original Workrave, WorkraveQt enforces breaks more strictly,
      making it harder to skip or postpone them. This helps ensure you actually
      take the breaks you need to stay healthy.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Configurable break intervals and durations</li>
      <li>Game/application detection to pause breaks</li>
      <li>System tray integration</li>
      <li>Visual timer display</li>
      <li>Cross-platform (Linux, Windows, macOS)</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
  
